messages.text: Thanks again for the ride man
No problem
Even though you got dirt all over my car lol
Sry about that
Where were u coming from?
Just heading home
Haha obviously, but why were you so dirty lol
Don’t worry about it
But thx for the ride, I really appreciate it
And sorry for getting dirt all over your car
It’s fine.
Oh my god u should turn on the news
Whats up?
A girl from ur high school went missing
I’m kind of busy right now, can’t watch
Omg I think it’s Tanya
Your Tanya
Dude aren’t you freaking out right now?
Tanya can’t be missing
I just saw her this afternoon
How recently? Her mom is saying she never came home from school
Wow this is fucked up, you need to call the police if you saw her
I’m not calling the police
And I didn’t really see her, just like in the hallway at school
We’ve been broken up for weeks we don’t really talk much
Oh my god this is so scary
I only sold her weed a couple of times but she seemed like such a nice girl
Can’t really talk now, but I’ll update you if I hear anything.
All right man, take it easy
Shit there really is a lot of dirt in my car.
Oh wow they found her car using GPS out near the fairgrounds
Shit really?
Were you with her?
Like when I picked u up down there, were you together?
Yes
What were you guys doing there? Did you leave her with someone?
I don’t really remember I was pretty high lol
Oh my god...
Stop texting me I don’t feel like talking
What were you guys doing? Who were u all with?
I told you I don’t really remember
You’re sick man
This is really freaky, how would you not remember what you were doing with your girlfriend?
She’s my ex-girlfriend, and I told you, we were pretty high
She didn’t want to drive so I called you for a ride
Why? We’re not even friends
Oof, ok bro that’s kind of harsh
I deal to you, but when have we ever hung out?
You’re a sick fucker, I know you’re lying to me
Don’t try to play me. I’ll tell the cops
Tell them what? You’re the one with dirt all over his car
You’re the one with a shovel still in the trunk
Shovel?
You put a ducking shovel in my trunk?!
You told me you were just putting your backpack in there
I gotta tell somebody, I can’t get involved in something like this
Haha ok you’re gonna go to the cops and tell them what?
They ask you how you know Tanya and you say, Oh I used to sell her weed. Great plan genius
I’m not gonna let you frame me for this shit
I can’t go to prison
Snitches get stitches, I thought that was your creed
Fuck you man, you don’t even know me
I’m not like that. Just cause I didn’t grow up in the rich-ass suburbs like you doesn’t mean I’m a criminal
Oh I forgot selling drugs was no longer a crime
Selling drugs will get you maybe a year or two. But what u did? That’s for life man
What I did? I don’t know what you’re talking about
I can’t get locked up forever. I have a family. I have a life.
What life? Selling weed and X to kids from the suburbs. That’s what you’re scared of losing?
Wow, you really are a pussy
And why would any cop believe you over me? The evidence is all over your car.
Your tire tracks are up and down the fairgrounds. You’re a goddamn drug dealer.
But me? I’m from the suburbs. I’ve never even met you for all they know.
You are so full of shit
How could you do this to me?
How could you do this to Tanya?
I did what had to be done. That’s it.
Clean your car. Go to sleep. Forget it in the morning.
Okay. Good night you sicko.
Oh btw, your facial hair in your drivers license picture is creepy AF
How do you know what my drivers license look like?
You left it in my car you dumb ass
GIVE IT TO ME!
Meet me at Crabbe Street with the license ASAP
Haha I don’t think so
Don’t make this mistake, Chris.
You don’t want to get involved with the police
I know shit about you, remember? I’ll tell them everything I know about you. About the drugs, about everything
Who will they believe?
I have to do the right thing
I can’t let you get away with this
I have the proof, you manipulative piece of shit
CHRIS!
DON’T YOU DARE!
CHRIS!
